Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先用過了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.58,0:02:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井先生需要的話  就點些什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.77,0:02:47.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…有早餐嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.12,0:02:48.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:03.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很感激筱塚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.96,0:03:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你沒有撕掉那封信的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.72,0:03:15.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前夜就見不到由綺了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.91,0:03:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白您說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.41,0:03:24.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成了我的女神
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就算是回禮了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.92,0:03:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這倒也不是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您看過演唱會了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.36,0:03:34.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是由綺小姐的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.60,0:03:36.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現實  對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.49,0:03:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是未來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:40.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我就是個礙事的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.92,0:03:41.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.76,0:03:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.52,0:03:48.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時就像這樣  一一提醒我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:51.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強人所難呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就告訴您一些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:03:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七瀨君  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:04:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯父  伯父
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.29,0:04:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的錯…因為我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:07.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.72,0:04:09.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快叫救護車
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.64,0:04:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先關掉煤氣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音樂節？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.00,0:04:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每年二月末召開  由東央電視台舉辦的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.05,0:04:27.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  那個我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.72,0:04:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫作明星  讀作維納斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.69,0:04:30.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維納斯音樂節
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啟明之星
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.88,0:04:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決出明日之星  年輕女性歌手限定的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.36,0:04:39.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我經常看的  但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.58,0:04:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  那…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺要在維納斯出場？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:45.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還並沒有決定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.89,0:04:49.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是報了名  並不一定會被選上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟由綺小姐才只出了一張單曲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:53.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果出場的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.63,0:04:54.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大衝擊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.40,0:04:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然就算出場也不等於穩坐明星之座
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.85,0:05:03.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但影響力一旦向全國蔓延  勢必會掀起一股風潮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:06.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲獎的話將更不可想像
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:12.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是檢驗我們事務所的能力的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最大的障礙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.41,0:05:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得理奈…小姐是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:20.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次也沒有出場過
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:22.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩次獲得出場機會  卻都剛好有別的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.75,0:05:27.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是她本人的意願？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.01,0:05:29.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不清楚  誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.41,0:05:31.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是緒方先生故意操作的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.88,0:05:33.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要與平庸之輩為伍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和平庸幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.82,0:05:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比試高下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  那他這次應該也不會同意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:54.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把維納斯的資料給我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.43,0:05:57.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還趕得上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.70,0:06:01.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說…他改變想法了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:03.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:04.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像他的作風
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.81,0:06:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像啊  很像緒方先生的作風
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:09.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他本來就那麼讓人琢磨不透吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.18,0:06:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後  突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.45,0:06:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是戰利品的收取
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.56,0:06:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那…之後？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈的話肯定能通過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.63,0:06:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能一起出場的話  由綺也一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.82,0:06:24.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.22,0:06:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個事務所限定只出場一人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然只是個慣例
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:33.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻是個不可打破的規矩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.51,0:06:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.96,0:06:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我寶貴的由綺…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺她知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.01,0:06:42.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不會想到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.84,0:06:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.35,0:06:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也沒有說過
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.75,0:06:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音樂節的事的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.05,0:06:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.57,0:06:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您也該想辦法…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:57.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這段戀情結束了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.89,0:07:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筱塚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.04,0:07:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有您的電話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請轉告說我已經回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筱塚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.64,0:07:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.81,0:07:14.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.86,0:07:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人溜躂著回去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:22.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您二位是家屬嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.02,0:07:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然已經聯繫過了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻只有電話留言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.79,0:07:31.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  居然是電話留言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.54,0:07:33.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大過年的還這麼忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:41.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯父為了我們…連料理都…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.59,0:07:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼和冬彌說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.17,0:07:48.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再哭喪著臉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓我後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.06,0:07:57.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先到先得  先到先得哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裏面的東西絕對夠份量
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:02.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓您吃虧的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.98,0:08:05.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  別擠了別擠了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:13.10,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}愛という形無いもの　とらわれている
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:20.74,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}心臓が止まるような恋が　あること知ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:29.01,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}会うたびに与えてくれた　憧れでさえ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:32.10,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}今でも信じて…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.25,0:08:13.10,inC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不知不覺  深陷愛的囚牢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:20.74,inC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我早已知道  愛會讓心臟停跳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:29.01,inC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}但渴望見你的衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:32.10,inC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}總讓我相信…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:40.83,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}お互いの気持ちはいつも　側にいるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.10,0:08:40.83,inC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}兩人的心意不會變  就在彼此身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:44.17,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}…のない情熱は
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:52.65,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}どこから来るの？どこかに眠っているのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:53.99,INJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}ララ　星が…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:44.17,inC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}不知不覺  深陷愛的囚牢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:20.74,inC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我早已知道  愛會讓心臟停跳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:29.01,inC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}但渴望見你的衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:32.10,inC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}總讓我相信…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.10,0:08:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論有幾張也…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被一幅畫召集起來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.98,0:09:21.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漲潮的時候到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.07,0:09:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙照顧了  弗蘭奇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.50,0:09:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  這副表情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.66,0:09:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我屈服了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.73,0:09:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  冬彌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:42.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井外出中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請在信號後…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我是七瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.49,0:09:48.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我打過來好幾次了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我現在在市立醫院
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:56.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上  伯父病情突然惡化
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:09:59.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收到消息後請趕快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.43,0:10:02.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.08,0:10:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有我們在的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.15,0:10:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.81,0:10:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彌生小姐  你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:26.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.49,0:10:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.10,0:10:29.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  趕快出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.50,0:11:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是血壓稍微有點高
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  剛好正月難得回家  美笑你們也在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:18.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸太興奮了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.83,0:11:20.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯父…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.81,0:11:23.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是沒什麼大事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.33,0:11:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有些檢查什麼的  就是手術可能要延後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.50,0:11:34.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.53,0:11:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他似乎非常沮喪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是無顏面對藤井君  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.14,0:11:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用這樣的  這也是沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.74,0:11:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.53,0:11:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前夜時在這裏見過的由綺的經紀人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.72,0:11:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去過echoes一次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.12,0:11:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井君不在的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:11:57.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她偶爾會來坐坐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.93,0:11:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是那裏氣氛很輕鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.19,0:12:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有別的客人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.13,0:12:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:03.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.05,0:12:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,店長說她經常接送你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺她…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.26,0:12:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計不知道吧  沒有談起過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.84,0:12:18.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前還以為是個可怕的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.47,0:12:22.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不光對由綺  對藤井君也很照顧呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.08,0:12:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之老爸似乎不用擔心了  我要回去一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.74,0:12:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美笑呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.69,0:12:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再待一會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.28,0:12:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是這樣  今天照X光時發現的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.11,0:13:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  要不要切說是要看今後檢查的情況
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起搏器？所以說…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.28,0:13:11.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探病嘛  突然大家一起來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.55,0:13:13.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老爸…你看  他會察覺到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.26,0:13:18.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  大伯你也很忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.52,0:13:25.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤倉小姐  請不要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.31,0:13:29.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我這知老又不服老的性格不好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.18,0:13:34.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了你  還撿回一條命
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.49,0:13:38.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手術延期了讓我鬆了口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.47,0:13:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說還要給我安「肉搏器」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.15,0:13:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是想想心臟好像就要停下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:46.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉搏？伯父…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.36,0:13:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你們兩人在我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.49,0:13:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和七瀨君好好相處…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.24,0:13:55.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.04,0:13:58.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬彌就請你忘掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:13:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.12,0:14:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請忘掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:15.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃晚飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就覺得很奇怪  這樣球不就掉到海裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.85,0:14:23.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不掉下去  絕對要打回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.76,0:14:26.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒打到掉下去怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就追加一百球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.21,0:14:28.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇哇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.74,0:14:31.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  那就來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:36.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等變得更暖和點了  再過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:38.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教我網球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  麻奈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.47,0:14:46.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼在冬彌的房間裏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.93,0:14:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.44,0:14:52.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才說A型的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  豎起耳朵聽好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是要去的朋友家碰巧在那附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.26,0:15:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前在簡歷上看到過  就覺得很近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.34,0:15:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友不在家…當然是女孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.53,0:15:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像和男朋友出去了  又是聖誕前夜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是就順路去看看而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.78,0:15:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好樵夫回來了  但我可沒在等他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.08,0:15:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過站在門外說話也不太好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.46,0:15:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得送他錄音電話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:25.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不設置好的話又有什麼意義
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.15,0:15:31.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤井現在外出中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.28,0:15:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請在信號音之後留下事情和名字
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.93,0:15:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我是由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.39,0:15:42.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…有點不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.65,0:15:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬彌君回家去了嗎  還是在醫院？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.49,0:15:51.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伯父身體怎麼樣了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.23,0:15:54.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能去探望真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正月也結束了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.71,0:16:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然由綺因為一直在工作沒什麼感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天晚上的話我在家
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.97,0:16:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果方便的話請打個電話來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:08.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…嗯  再見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.65,0:16:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在進入正題之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:28.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來的路上沒有被跟蹤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:32.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彌生小姐  我來…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.63,0:16:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.79,0:16:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,維納斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.15,0:16:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  墨水省下了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.18,0:16:59.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.65,0:17:02.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老糊塗了嗎  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.04,0:17:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明到今天為止連提都不提一個字的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.11,0:17:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想出場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.07,0:17:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想  一直都想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.69,0:17:15.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要怎麼辦  應該是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原則是一家事務所只能派一人出場
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:21.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者一個組合
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.30,0:17:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於兩人平分秋色的我社來說
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.21,0:17:25.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是讓人煩惱的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.76,0:17:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事…可…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話答案不是已經出來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.83,0:17:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點猶豫都不用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.12,0:17:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說  那是為了由綺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.97,0:17:41.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.28,0:17:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  我遵從決定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.33,0:17:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  正相反吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:53.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天起  緒方理奈從緒方事務所獨立
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:59.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  這次又能為我省下些什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.12,0:18:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唱片的出版費
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.36,0:18:06.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是最後的工作  拜託送我回公寓
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.51,0:18:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.93,0:18:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.95,0:18:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒方先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.75,0:18:16.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.78,0:18:24.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.00,0:18:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒打算去音樂節什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.85,0:18:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.86,0:18:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緒方先生  你不阻止她嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.29,0:19:02.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彌生小姐  你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:05.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼能這麼平靜  理奈都要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.11,0:19:07.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說要不幹了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.55,0:19:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.26,0:19:11.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送我  帶我去理奈那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.05,0:19:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請在下面等我  我去把車子開過來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.98,0:19:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.91,0:19:28.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目標是那邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您竟然察覺到了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:36.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是平良木君嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.50,0:19:37.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.74,0:19:41.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拍下你們的照片  他想幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:42.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.05,0:19:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝作不知道  或是準備付諸法律
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.57,0:19:49.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.99,0:19:51.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.86,0:19:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.88,0:19:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青年呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:19:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.10,0:20:01.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對由綺不利的話  我可絕不原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.48,0:20:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈小姐應該也幫了一次忙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.13,0:21:07.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不要被擊垮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.32,0:21:15.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是緒方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.59,0:21:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小英  是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然是神崎社長  竟然能追我到這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.29,0:21:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一會兒能見個面嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.98,0:21:34.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,社長  瑪瑙小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.85,0:22:23.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理奈！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.71,0:22:28.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  我是由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.92,0:22:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.15,0:22:37.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由綺
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.67,0:24:22.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十七頁
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.38,0:24:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望被揭穿的謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.61,0:24:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和希望不被相信的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.34,0:24:30.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各有一個
